  "test_disclosure": "The immutable test has been observed for earlier candidates. Its aggregate gate and source-level failure patterns motivated collecting new disjoint licensed field sources, but no test image, label, logit, duplicate, per-example failure, calibration value, or threshold enters training, checkpoint selection, temperature fitting, or hierarchy fitting. The numerical promotion gates remain unchanged.",
